snippet.title: SmartLess
snippet.description: "SmartLess" is a comedy-based podcast starring Sean Hayes, Jason Bateman & Will Arnett. The conceit of the show is that for each episode, one of the three hosts brings on a guest that is a surprise to the other two hosts.  What ensues is an organic, casual, laugh-filled discussion whereby the hosts and the listeners learn something new from or about the guest that they never knew before. Guests, so far, have included Will Ferrell, Dax Shepard, Robert Downey, Jr., Maya Rudolph, Senator Kamala Harris, Seth Rogen, Melissa McCarthy and Neil deGrasse Tyson. Dozens of other huge and interesting guests are forthcoming.
